### One-command install (run anywhere, works with fresh or existing NanoClaw)

```bash
curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/profbernardoj/nano-everclaw/main/setup.sh | bash
```

Then go to your NanoClaw folder and let Claude do the rest:

```bash
cd ~/nanoclaw          # or wherever you cloned it
