/add-morpheus          # â† this is the new skill auto-added by setup
```

Claude will automatically:
- Patch the container runner to reach the host proxy (handles `host.docker.internal` on macOS, gateway on Linux/Docker)
- Enable hybrid mode: keep Claude for agent orchestration & swarms, route heavy lifting to Morpheus (GLM-5 default, Kimi K2.5, Qwen3, etc.)
- Add MOR staking commands inside the agent
- Register status tool

Restart NanoClaw (or just say â€œrestartâ€ in the main channel) and youâ€™re done.

Your WhatsApp agent now runs on decentralized inference â€” stake MOR once, never pay per token again.

